### Get user profile (replace {{token}} with actual token from login response)
GET http://localhost:8098/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8098/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all users including soft-deleted
GET http://localhost:8098/users?includeDeleted=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:8098/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "gender": "MALE",
  "dob": "1990-01-01",
  "phoneNumber": "0912345678",
  "address": "123 Main St",
  "image": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg",
  "roles": []
}

### Get user by ID (replace :id with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update user (replace :id with actual user ID)
PUT http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fullName": "John Updated",
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "credits": 100
}

### Soft delete user (replace :id with actual user ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Permanent delete user (replace :id with actual user ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011?hard=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restore deleted user (replace :id with actual user ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add credits to user (replace :id with actual user ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/credits
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 50
}

### Assign roles to user (replace :id with actual user ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8098/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roleIds": ["507f1f77bcf86cd799439011", "507f1f77bcf86cd799439012"]
}